title: Jebby LFT Silver/Gold+
body:
Looking for a team. 

Silver Mid/Jungle/ADC main, have never taken ranked seriously, mainly int but reformed and looking for some people to play with.
Soloing has cause me to become toxic and I find if i duo i am fine.

Either 5v5 or duos. 
Keen for anything. 

Thank you guys. hit me up. always available.
